Capital Group International Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 7:24 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Capital Group International Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Capital Group International Inc. is an asset management holding company of The Capital Group Companies, Inc. Through its subsidiaries, the firm provides its services to individuals, institutions, corporations, governments, public funds, endowments, and foundations. It manages separate client focused portfolios and mutual funds. The firm invests in the public equity and alternative investment markets across the globe. It was founded on December 16, 1987 and is based in Los Angeles, California with an additional office in Los Angeles, California. Capital Group International Inc. operates as a subsidiary of The Capital Group Companies, Inc.


11100 Santa Monica Boulevard15th FloorLos Angeles, CA 90025-3384United StatesFounded in 1987










