			Welcome		
International Capital is a leading full service U.S. real estate investment company offering domestic and international high net worth individuals, family offices and institutional investors opportunities to invest in partnerships which match their investment strategy targeting exceptional results with risk-mitigated returns.
Our service portfolio includes:

Well structured Investments as Private Placements:Real Estate, Land Investments, Royalty Investments and Renewable Energy Projects
Real Estate Asset and Property Management
Acquisition and Disposition
Restructuring and workout
European Capital market access and consulting
US-Greencard EB-5 investment opportunities

 You can find more details in the services section   or    download our company portrait or performance history.  
